**/circuits/input.json
**/circuits/address_hash.hex

# --- Soroban test snapshots (generados al correr los tests) ---
**/test_snapshots/

# --- Modelos de face-api (pesados; se bajan con `npm run download-models`) ---
identity/issuer/matcher/models/

# --- Estado local del issuer (commitments + hashes de de-dup, NO es PII) ---
identity/issuer/.issuer-state.json

# --- Coordinación entre agentes (no es código del producto) ---
.comms/

# --- SO / editor ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
/web/vite.config.js
/web/vite.config.d.ts

# --- Deploy local (ids + secretos efímeros de testnet) ---
/.deploy/

# --- tesseract.js: datos de idioma (se descargan solos) ---
**/*.traineddata
**/*.traineddata.gz

# --- artefactos del circuito servidos al frontend (se copian con copy-circuit.sh) ---
/web/public/circuits/

# --- Plataforma CAPA 2 (store local, no PII) ---
platform/api/.platform-store.json
/web/public/circuits-platform/
